{"data":{"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"EthPhoto","cover":null,"tech":["Ethereum","IPFS","React","Solidity","Web3.js"],"github":"https://github.com/aniketbiswas21/EthPhoto","external":"","cta":null},"html":"<p>A decentralized application for geo-tagged media sharing on Ethereum blockchain. Implemented Ethereum-IPFS hybrid storage solution for efficient decentralized media storage with location metadata, enabling censorship-resistant photo sharing. Built a responsive React-based web interface with Metamask integration for wallet connectivity.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Data Partitioning Framework","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/d2194/demo.png","srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/cebcc/demo.png 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/272cf/demo.png 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/d2194/demo.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/9aa63/demo.avif 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/e6db6/demo.avif 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/f47db/demo.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/240e7/demo.webp 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/faefe/demo.webp 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/d5dc4/demo.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":438}}},"tech":["JavaScript","React","Azure","TypeScript","Performance Optimization"],"github":null,"external":null,"cta":null},"html":"<p>Designed and implemented a foundational data partitioning framework that supports multiple concurrent application instances in a shared JavaScript runtime. This system significantly improved performance and reliability for Microsoft Viva Connections applications, supporting millions of users across enterprise environments. The architecture enabled isolated state management while maintaining optimization for shared resources.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Viva Connections Mobile","cover":null,"tech":["React Native","TypeScript","REST APIs","GraphQL","Azure","Performance Optimization"],"github":"","external":"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-viva/connections","cta":null},"html":"<p>Led architecture and development of core components for Microsoft Viva Connections Mobile from early prototypes to a enterprise platform serving 7M+ monthly active users. Implemented advanced data partitioning and caching strategies that decreased load times by 40% and reduced memory consumption by 35%. Designed and built the Operator Insights engine enabling real-time analytics for tenant administrators across global deployments.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Developer Productivity Toolkit","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/d2194/halcyon.png","srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/cebcc/halcyon.png 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/272cf/halcyon.png 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/d2194/halcyon.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/9aa63/halcyon.avif 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/e6db6/halcyon.avif 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/f47db/halcyon.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/240e7/halcyon.webp 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/faefe/halcyon.webp 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3b4d6e8f44baf7e6d7a0ed4b3e4d8d39/d5dc4/halcyon.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":438}}},"tech":["TypeScript","Node.js","Azure","GitHub Actions","Webpack"],"github":"","external":"","cta":null},"html":"<p>Created comprehensive developer toolkit that reduced development cycles by 60+ hours monthly across engineering teams. Built automated diagnostics and debugging tools that accelerated feature delivery by identifying and resolving bottlenecks early in the development process. Implemented configurable code generation system that standardized implementations across multiple components.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"High-Performance Link Resolution","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/d2194/demo.png","srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/cebcc/demo.png 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/272cf/demo.png 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/d2194/demo.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/9aa63/demo.avif 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/e6db6/demo.avif 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/f47db/demo.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/240e7/demo.webp 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/faefe/demo.webp 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/3936989a99991beb6d649d7a7039df60/d5dc4/demo.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":438}}},"tech":["Node.js","TypeScript","Azure Functions","Redis","Performance Optimization"],"github":"","external":"","cta":null},"html":"<p>Built high-performance link resolution system processing millions of requests with 99.9% reliability. Implemented advanced caching strategies with Redis that reduced response times by 70% and decreased database load significantly. Designed resilient fallback mechanisms ensuring consistent performance even during partial system failures.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Operator Insights Engine","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/bc3b9/course-card.png","srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/9a130/course-card.png 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/a3fa1/course-card.png 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/bc3b9/course-card.png 700w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/87926/course-card.png 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/dae43/course-card.avif 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/d7667/course-card.avif 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/7ec1a/course-card.avif 700w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/71a30/course-card.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/5d873/course-card.webp 175w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/26a00/course-card.webp 350w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/f23f0/course-card.webp 700w,\n/PortfolioByBChiang/static/4e06bd39766c182ea26b255309b1dee1/2c2d0/course-card.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":394}}},"tech":["React","TypeScript","Azure","Real-time Analytics","Data Visualization"],"github":null,"external":"","cta":null},"html":"<p>Designed and built the Operator Insights Engine architecture for Microsoft Viva, enabling real-time analytics and data-driven decision-making for tenant administrators. This system processes millions of data points to provide actionable insights on platform usage, performance metrics, and user engagement.</p>\n<p>The architecture leverages Azure services to deliver scalable analytics capabilities with minimal latency, supporting interactive dashboards and proactive monitoring for enterprise customers. Implemented sophisticated data aggregation algorithms that maintain privacy compliance while delivering valuable business intelligence.tle: 'Build a Spotify Connected App'\ncover: './course-card.png'\nexternal: '<a href=\"https://www.newline.co/courses/build-a-spotify-connected-app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.newline.co/courses/build-a-spotify-connected-app</a>'\ncta: '<a href=\"https://www.newline.co/courses/build-a-spotify-connected-app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.newline.co/courses/build-a-spotify-connected-app</a>'\ntech:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>React</li>\n<li>Express</li>\n<li>Spotify API</li>\n<li>Styled Components</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>Having struggled with understanding how the Spotify OAuth flow works, I made the course I wish I could have had.</p>\n<p>Unlike tutorials that only cover a few concepts and leave you with half-baked GitHub repositories, this course covers everything from explaining the principles of REST APIs to implementing Spotify's OAuth flow and fetching API data in a React app. By the end of the course, you’ll have an app deployed to the internet you can add to your portfolio.</p>"}}]}}}